{"tid":2400794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"炮台山女子過馬路疑攝車罅 遭電車撞困車底","createTime":"2021-02-09T08:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T09:07:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9317bc26d74db106280c9ef5fc8582120eb17bae","tid":2400794,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AUqmv_Zi0f-x7_4KgsOKHLpS2m4=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HKUEOMESDZH2XNINWMSH7UFGOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAUqmv_Zi0f-x7_4KgsOKHLpS2m4%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHKUEOMESDZH2XNINWMSH7UFGOM.jpg&h=063d0a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北角英皇道西行線港鐵炮台山站對開，下午2時許，一名61歲女子過馬路時，遭一輛電車的右邊車身撞倒，夾在車底。消防接報趕至將她救出，她右腳骨折，右手受傷，事後由救護車送往東區醫院，情況一度危殆，經治理後已告穩定。現場遺下一灘血迹，警員正調查交通意外原因。現場消息稱，懷疑有人「攝車罅」胡亂過馬路，遭駛至電車撞倒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210203/IRBGKTS4JVEVXDPTQLNDXKWE3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210203%2FIRBGKTS4JVEVXDPTQLNDXKWE3Y%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=7ffd717e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210203%2FIRBGKTS4JVEVXDPTQLNDXKWE3Y%2F&h=2d831736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210203/IRBGKTS4JVEVXDPTQLNDXKWE3Y/</a>"},{"pid":"683575843280fdcf5506b12437eaddbd5df1da77","tid":2400794,"uid":759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"車唔死殘廢就最好"},{"pid":"48fad66b761f64907fc42177ce2d95f18b2984fe","tid":2400794,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點會俾電車撞"},{"pid":"efb636d876658b361ecb2d503bfd08489c47bf30","tid":2400794,"uid":67500,"lik